  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>Fleming</span> <span>2026-06-28 10:00</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p>以下文章来源于：新周刊</p>\n  <strong>新周刊</strong>\n  <p>中国最新锐的生活方式周刊。</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=af48b6a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeGYtoGHZ33II5u1tibcFs5JVTc7ibn23GgBdhXxoUia3BsG4D7rsmpC650fKdk3yaLeaP6Vic7zNWCgtT0zhgFbnPYFicqmp8AhmiaHk%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"height: 308px;width: 578px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/o02wSnKAPeETSfrZKiadauHpNzdtsgicz44K1wk0Pj9UlOSGsFeSef1oAc5abkQ2MY9p7UBPQ8hkOoX5icWyChvBaFChYm8UhbkG1Lgst7Qd30/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"308\" data-imgfileid=\"101409872\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=57d2667c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fo02wSnKAPeETSfrZKiadauHpNzdtsgicz44K1wk0Pj9UlOSGsFeSef1oAc5abkQ2MY9p7UBPQ8hkOoX5icWyChvBaFChYm8UhbkG1Lgst7Qd30%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.06666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"height: 39px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"39\" data-imgfileid=\"101298595\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d8a30ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0Lereibp3GVwr7pAWURUC5MH7xdLsTMSsaiayEzicByDcKTBHnpsGXGoTVQQ5Iyw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdkswp16e7\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdkswv1aeq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">从十年前那张因为长相而改变命运的脸，到如今被奉为神作的字迹、儿戏般的婚育传闻，在关于范小勤的网络喧嚣中，他依然是当年那个毫无知觉地卷入流量漩涡的孩子，改变的似乎只有旁人借他收割流量与财富的由头。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.08888888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" data-imgfileid=\"101298596\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d266c885&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQDFNHs0vUhrvC75JRXlG0rM2iat53EoZMsodUxkMSYWXNSIFUEeuo2I89A9ibZcCic1oNlHEWLAxeWpFZgeic0wdtg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.024074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: 14px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"25\" data-imgfileid=\"101298593\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aedec240&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0LereibplkrJOvk6R1Efiaq0NlWibAtLj0DDlMWGggbQ9KdrLibUvZbz91W4FNd7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: right;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">文</span></span></strong><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></span></strong><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">Fleming</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: right;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑</span></strong><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></strong><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;visibility: visible;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">腾宇</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: right;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">来源｜</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">新周刊（ID：new-weekly）</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: right;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">封面来源</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">小马云表哥视频截图</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">在习惯了今天造神、明天就毁掉的互联网，谁能想到那个曾经因为一张特殊的脸被推上风口浪尖的范小勤，会在这个夏天以一种近乎荒诞的姿态，重新占领全网的视线。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">引爆这轮狂欢的，是一张宣纸和一杆毛笔。视频里的少年顶着一头扎眼的棕红卷发，站在桌前，用力、缓慢地，在纸上留下三个字：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">“范小勤”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.5814814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409857\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9c155966&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeEurUY7w3hpSRp496TdQEtGTJ4c1ImdfcBria4KNosYmLPK9mk7ol1Lia2Jgz08r1TjCM7ic22J4Y4JZCBicJbo3uMgCiccrerBAWzY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdov6h1j0m\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdov6mk4b\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">（图/社交媒体截图）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">不知是谁先发现了“勤”字左边草字头，隐约能看出人形轮廓。接下来，事态有了爆炸式的发展，各路“野生鉴赏家”纷纷下场，用尽毕生所学，试图为这“旷世奇作”赋予深远意义。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">有人说，那是韩愈举手遥指，柳宗元侧身而立，苏轼兄弟三人前后相随，王安石曾巩一前一后，分明就是一幅“唐宋八大家骑牛游春图”。甚至赞其“一笔出八仙，逍遥似神游”“他把自己写得很小，却把勤劳写得很大”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">也有分析说这叫“稚拙”，是未被技法污染过的天然境界。言下之意，颜柳欧赵反而落了俗套。也难怪众多二创视频呼吁“新手入门不建议临摹范公，可以选择难度低一点的比如王羲之字帖入手。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0.5em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdpfpv10k5\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6620370370370371\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(240, 240, 240) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409858\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=82a3110d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeFwHASWCLNZ2YhnYOPWtf7cpQvbLIeXpTdesUmia1Nq08icblthOaibwJiccKavkjJLPic2nQB5ebJdcxPfYAbr93DpBFvuTUicZpDUU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdpoq6ga5\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">“很高兴你也喜欢书法，并有自己的见解。”（图/社交媒体截图）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">跳脱这些讨论，这件事本身的荒诞程度，已经超过了任何一条评论所能触及的边界。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">随之而来的是一场电商奇迹。在其表哥团队运营的直播间里，这些附带五指山手印的墨宝，被标价175元至228元不等。短短几场直播，名为“范小勤书法手工八大家”的商品售出近3000单，甚至一度冲上了家居饰品榜单的榜首。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">然而，这场“神仙书法”掀起的风波还未散去，更具视觉和伦理冲击的剧情已接连上演。几天前，范小勤19岁的女友“小鬼”自曝怀孕，且声称“双方父母都很支持”；但两天以后，范小勤又被拉出来，煞有介事地宣布“都是假的”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">人们心知肚明，范小勤既不懂什么是“八仙”，更无法理解婚姻与抚养的意义。他只是木讷地坐在镜头前，染着五颜六色的头发，机械地配合着指令搞笑，用不同的话题激荡网民审丑猎奇的诉求。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.3351851851851853\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409859\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3fafe760&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeHiaaLP7yuv2ygwkqhWCPpZGgaicPWqB2R7KNSen2wDuWgj71Br2GGxQCuWDp1wSF5Src4qicbibOoNphMvFVLS1j96iczibSNcM6a6Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 48px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdq5r4pv2\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdq5ra1lu2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">（图/小马云表哥视频截图）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3750\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101296245\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6f13e36e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vYs92nHCpdbueQF7gdhICh6n4bg74ZZBRll6JriaDqWuAUKCORW2pdPf2yVUIWtCJ5r1TYvaDtK5CA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdqswx24k3\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdqsx419gt\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 52, 198);font-weight: bold;\">被流量反复选中的“撞脸少年”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">范小勤这个名字，很多人已经陌生了。但“小马云”三个字，大约还能在网民记忆里激起一点涟漪。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">范小勤今年18岁。他的故事，从7岁那年就不再只属于他自己。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">2015年，他住在江西吉安永丰县一个叫严辉村的地方。彼时，范小勤的家庭状况，用“家徒四壁”来形容都显得有些奢侈。父母残疾，哥哥范小勇同样认知障碍，仅靠低保和家里微薄的劳作勉强维持生计。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">然而，命运的齿轮，开始以一种不可思议的方式转动起来。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">那年春节，远房表哥黄新龙回乡探亲，随手拍了几张范小勤的照片传到网上。网友发现，这孩子的五官，几乎就是马云的幼年翻版。马云本人也在微博上调侃说还以为是家里人上传了自己小时候的照片。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">这一句话，让“小马云”的称号响彻全国。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">一时间，范小勤的家门前车水马龙，媒体、爱心人士、博主纷至沓来。他们带来了食物、衣物、慰问金，也带来了无休止的围观。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">依稀记得，当时网上不少人感叹小马云的境遇是贫困家庭出路，是“围观改变社会”的体现。这种朴素的愿望，在流量的裹挟下，显得既真实又脆弱，也为后来的故事埋下了伏笔。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">2017年，有商人以“资助教育”的名义，将范小勤带往河北石家庄。从此，范小勤告别了泥泞的乡村，出门有豪车接送，身边有专职保姆照料，不仅出入各种晚宴、商演、综艺节目，甚至参演了电影《雾路奇途》。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.3111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409861\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=65fd9e98&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeECITRTlsGbM63iaXxWlTw3xh4vS3VC9P8XMw4M5jUaMQKj6tbFHGkTenKibaMoBQwuLkGujD38ezrmLYYgjGAK99V2oWA390HrQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdrzmsdoq\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdrzmy1t96\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">2017年上映电影《雾路奇途》（图/豆瓣截图）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">被包装成“小马总”的四年里，范小勤从未真正走进课堂。他长期缺课，被频繁带着辗转于各地拍视频，不过学会了面对镜头抱拳致谢，以及那句“阿里巴巴，芝麻开门。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">命运的馈赠，早已在暗中标好了价格，但这价格，对于范小勤来说是无法承受之重。随着年龄的增长，范小勤的外貌与马云的相似度越来越低，他的“商业价值”也随之骤降。2021年，他被解约送回老家。随后，严酷的现实摆在眼前：被鉴定为智力二级残疾，并确诊患有矮小症，认知水平仍停留在低龄儿童阶段。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">通常这类悲剧故事到这里本该画上句号。但互联网的神奇与残酷就在于，它总能找到新的切入点。2022年后，范小勤的表哥接手相关账号的运营，不再包装“总裁”神话，而是转向了更契合短视频生态的土味日常。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409862\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bb41cf1a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeGPF227DHM9OebmaGjTdBQzA1Sp80CpFdaAurdWXPBOcO7FutbryafaFJOQCBz6gH3QRwy7jaWz6dvUZybBCGSsCebmPy9VVibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdsg5j1s31\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdsg5o92c\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">（图/《楚门的世界》）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">如今，已经成年的范小勤，再次被推到了台前。这一次，他不再靠长相。2026年5月，范小勤开启了成年后的第一场直播，在线人数一度破7万。他顶着锡纸烫的棕红卷发，对着镜头一遍遍道谢。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.7055555555555555\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409863\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e14b4109&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeEKS9q7UflLKJKPZxcXxupdpUCtE3rezjWMDNzXVltSCVGGfSem8LLhLHJAaNVAdV6NYZ9Cnlic3Nfq1BsrnmxdlqqTOiaDXE7N4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdt75d385\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdt75if3a\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">（图/小马云表哥视频截图）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 48px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">评论区里说：“光是谢礼物，都快谢累了。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3750\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101296246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=42f04bbb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vYs92nHCpdbueQF7gdhICh6MebCYnvZdvTDPbOUA7ibvzc0o3YBuC9FURHiaKksE5qUFLohPK7nDqRQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdts5v1o6h\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdts611n3b\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 52, 198);font-weight: bold;\">谁在为“拙作”买单？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">如果说范小勤早年的走红是一场意外，那么他的再度“翻红”更具策略性，可谓充满了互联网后现代的荒诞与黑色幽默。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">比如网友关于签名的解读，以范小勤涂写的字叠加自己一本正经胡说八道的二创，共同完成一次抽象的集体创作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7268518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409864\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f79fcdb2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeFyUWtO7oHicTGticEtQ8v4hzS4rcQUFAiaCB00pgezZOicdmZ5g4FicbXbpGLBY4PZxDEMrnic6lCYbcaDPEsROrrXD1DDavJWMficeU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwduhrsmqg\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwduhrygab\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);font-weight: normal;\">（图/社交媒体截图）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">直播镜头前的范小勤，语气自然得仿佛资深主播，丝毫看不出当年青涩局促的痕迹。他直白地表达着“想赚钱买房、想娶老婆”的欲望，说曾经独自乘坐火车前往云南，手捧玫瑰花与网红“奔现”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">无论是真情流露还是剧本安排，都足够让人眼前一黑，然后忍不住多看两眼。一个被命运反复抛掷的少年，在成年后展现出对世俗生活的渴望，这种“真实”与“不真实”之间的模糊与矛盾，也让看客们在同情与审视之间反复横跳，贡献宝贵的停留时长。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">而那张爆红的“一笔出八仙”签名，更是这场审丑逻辑的巅峰之作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">成年，是一个精心选择的时间节点。在此之前，范小勤不能独立直播打赏，平台对未成年人有诸多限制。而18岁这道门槛一迈过去，他作为一个反复以出格姿态引发关注、大部分网民都认识的网络符号，可变现能力发生了质的变化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.7185185185185186\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409865\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=28329d6b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeFqjkiaFgVia1LtNDcrF3ldDn9RxbW94zXbWHg6J4vSdSd6zKA8iaqXPn8jEdB1hN5knSUF3YcibjJaYBDZY56I8AkbrTwU5kNovG4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdvd6ccw5\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdvd6i1vgh\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">我不知道他们到底是怎么了。（图/小马云表哥视频截图）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">208元的书法签名，定价不高不低，既有让普通人产生冲动消费的可能，又足以制造可观的成交量。假设成交情况属实，大多数人下单的驱动力应该更接近于搞抽象。毕竟“唐宋八大家游春图”这个梗，在某些评论区甚至比名家真迹更有社交货币的流通效力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">花钱等于表明我懂这个“烂活”，没有一个人在正经认可这幅字及其作者的价值。所有人的行为叠加在一起，共同制造出了一个书法大师范小勤，并让一个有认知障碍的18岁少年，以这个荒诞的名义完成了自己第一次规模化变现。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdvvgk52o\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.7222222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(240, 240, 240) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409866\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8aa70059&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeFIdic8vo72ufNoGxN82NP1owG6hYyEGRIibicyLBvaAMmWtdwV4bdVtnn91RcFKVmgdbKALYKV7f7bW50icGIcste1MoW0NKVWkMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdw6st1u7z\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdw6sy20o9\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">“墨宝”二级市场行情火热。（图/二手电商截图）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">书法签名的热度还没完全散去，“小马云要当爸爸了”的词条就挂上了各大平台热搜，等热度差不多了，团队两天之后又发视频称“都是假的”。从网恋相识、自曝双胞胎再到辟谣，前后两个月，每一步都踩在流量最密集、讨论最激烈的地方。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">纵观评论区，人们无疑是愤怒的。一个智力鉴定为二级残疾、连钱的面额都分不清的人，他真的理解“女朋友”“恋爱”“生孩子”这些词意味着什么吗？也有感叹和带着某种说不清来由的祝愿——他原生家庭那么难，如果真的能有人陪，也许是命运给他的一点补偿。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">而调动了如此多情绪的主角范小勤，根本不知道也不可能思考，这个世界正在发生什么。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">在如今的中文互联网上，严肃正在全面溃败，取而代之的是以“抽象”为代表的解构热潮。看客们用最天花乱坠的词语去堆砌一个智力残疾者的缺陷，通过这种极端的反差，来消解主流审美和精英文化的严肃性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">这是互联网一种典型的“电子宠物”心态。当他写字时，他被捧为“稚拙派大师”；当他传出恋爱绯闻时，他又成了满足下沉市场窥私欲的“爽剧男主”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">在关于小马云的表哥的争论中，最常见的一种声音是：“流量至少给了他一笔固定收入，让他能吃饱穿暖”。正如他表哥在采访中所言，“有人消费是好事，我们不拍，他就是在外边流浪。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.6428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"406\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"406\" data-backh=\"667\" data-imgfileid=\"101409867\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=68a50ca0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fo02wSnKAPeHQicCnfgA7AXbUMCKkRGANiapVsz8QDLWBHBCFzINJOM1pepBYHpmZyTnvp0bTwTiaUrMbfmCznkBk8HJO8Waw4ibniboOTppUlmIU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdwwy61hvn\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdwwyb12z0\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">（图/凤凰weekly）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">算法及其幕后推手成功地让大众相信，除了出卖自己的残缺与隐私，这个孩子在世界上没有第二条活路，把一种带有剥削性质的围观，合理化为了底层唯一的救赎。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 48px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">每个人都在这场消费中得到了满足——团队赚到了真金白银，观众们收获了乐子与同情，而范小勤呢？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3750\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101296247\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9c1ff179&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vYs92nHCpdbueQF7gdhICh69wicwdn3toUy1ib4ibVYZAHQXc4c9XqWjVkuIuz4WTgftXHEwpbIRia8KA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdxdjc9yd\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdxdjj1krj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 52, 198);font-weight: bold;\">世界，终究是个巨大的马戏团？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">几乎每隔一月，互联网上就会涌现出一批靠“反常规”走红的面孔。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409868\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=83a38d95&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeHPPs2FMZAvgniao4S6WE43DzpC5nYg3ZiaYqVgiamL8fqpiaFD21YPHULUGKJsQLHibcB6LUCJfoOnNbl96v7Fq3BcoryKjhEB5icoE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdy4fk1g7p\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdy4fpkm1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">（图/小马云表哥视频截图）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">你总能刷到，或至少刷到不止一个在直播间里展现失序生活、被网友调侃为“电子宠物”的各路土味红人。TA们走红的节点各不相同，可以是一首歌，可以是一张脸，可以是一个怪异的口头禅，但走红之后发生的事情，几乎如出一辙：剥离掉现实社会背景中沉重的苦难，只提取最具视觉冲击力或娱乐性的碎片，将其包装成一种独特的梗供大众反复玩乐，直到审美疲劳或舆论走向反噬，最终被无情迭代。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">然后下一个幸运儿或者受害者，出现了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0.5em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdyqmn10bu\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7175925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(240, 240, 240) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409869\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d657ab6c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeEbSSh9P1q5QxlNRE1eCKAeHHo3Mvxp0BscLraflEKibxQS0PT98KQlN4wN2QaPJyzeLdgwgXmKxJHRwwmN9dC47yTV52I1SV5U%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdyxpwlav\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdyxq1879\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">（图/社交媒体截图）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">这类内容的生存空间，其实一直处于某种微妙的收窄之中。直播行业监管趋严，平台的合规压力在增加。2026年以来，多个平台相继推出“特殊群体保护机制”，对疑似认知障碍主播的开播设置了监护人确认要求。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">范小勤的成年首播其实已经触碰了监管的边界，并引发了相当一部分网友的公开质疑，说明公众对这类内容的容忍阈值逐渐降低。许多人不再纯粹审丑猎奇，而是在复杂的互联网抱有难得的清醒和悲悯。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">但监管和舆论压力或许能改变流量的流向，未必能改变它的本质。当一类内容受到限制，注意力会迅速转向另一类形式相似、只是换了包装的内容。审丑流量的根不在内容本身，而是一种以围观他人生命为娱乐的文化习惯。这种习惯的形成，远比任何单一内容的出现都古老。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8546296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409870\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c7ca1b39&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeGibXTTzyMA9Via1aG2hWLXjvaWfiaZCGBfW0NGfhKonlThhdIqcD5qG9PNYVNnHMAwxZ8LfVyEqboic2Zibu3w0Od70XF1tQnlxY8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwdzkkq7zr\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwdzkkvey5\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">脑洞大开的“唐宋八大家骑牛游春图”（图/社交媒体）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">短期内，范小勤的直播热度还会维持一段时间，起码评论区的二创段子、梗图正在以惊人的速度继续生产。然后热度慢慢下降，像潮水一样悄无声息地消退。等到下一个节点出现，也许是他第一次去某个城市，也许是哥哥的某个新动态，也许是范小勤又学了什么新东西被拍下来传开了——流量会再度短暂涌入，然后再退去。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">这个堪称当代互联网定律的循环，在范小勤身上已经被验证了至少三次。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">范小勤的“奇幻漂流”或许只是互联网时代大潮中的一朵浪花，但它值得每一个刷到视频的人想一想：我们到底在消费什么？我们又被什么所消费？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">范小勤的故事，从2015年那张照片算起，已经持续了整整十一年。十一年里，他从来算不上主角，只是像一块被反复举起、反复丢下的砖，用力拍在世界头上，围观的喝彩响起。每次举起来，拍下去，都有人宣布他是幸运的，他被看见了，人们短暂地投以关注，并热切期待下一次可以消费的网络奇观。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"2.5083333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101409871\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9ccb3ca2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeFCmCRVeIOOEJRnJXAEmJibHNJzVjnfhdMLzv75vyhj6ib1VyiblmIlrzczK4SNFZw7jvaQAz7J36OOYzxdeR2rDqjR04c7z0es0k%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mqwe03ip1cj4\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mqwe03iu18vr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">（图/《霸王别姬》）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 48px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">可是，被看见，从来不等于被善待。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.06666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: 39px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"51\" data-imgfileid=\"101298594\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd023431&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0LereibpOTKhlQucdMlnua1EZPEftBTh3iaNT7QPQlFYa6jHJ58VcEIpc2SXg7A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.06666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);height: 39px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"51\" data-imgfileid=\"101298598\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=62a9ba52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0LereibpaO1bAicFfUgxRicmVz0WLEJINuCCErEc1KS2r8fuFZCicO3END8ibSE2Ng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDk5NzA0Mw==&amp;mid=2248892962&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=91994e66d16e46f5ff33978fa071095a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/o02wSnKAPeGxicNns3Eic0wtE8puLzv9wTiaUSmIZV9mUCliaghu8jjUicQiabTwTWt053n2N3X3gJQ0BCzrxcvEJhfN0EsTcN6bunro55qkJDuzg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23333333333333334\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/o02wSnKAPeGxicNns3Eic0wtE8puLzv9wTiaUSmIZV9mUCliaghu8jjUicQiab